te Colonels Logo</div></a></article><article class="lw-mini-logo-card"><a href="https://logos-world.net/danganronpa-logo/" class="lw-mini-logo-link"><div class="lw-mini-logo-thumb" role="img" aria-label="Danganronpa Logo" style="background-image:url(&#039;https://logos-world.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Danganronpa-Logo-120x67.png&#039;);"></div><div class="lw-mini-logo-title">Danganronpa Logo</div></a></article><article class="lw-mini-logo-card"><a href="https://logos-world.net/discover-logo/" class="lw-mini-logo-link"><div class="lw-mini-logo-thumb" role="img" aria-label="Discover Logo" style="background-image:url(&#039;https://logos-world.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Discover-Logo-120x67.png&#039;);"></div><div class="lw-mini-logo-title">Discover Logo</div></a></article><article class="lw-mini-logo-card"><a href="https://logos-world.net/indianapolis-colts-logo/" class="lw-mini-logo-link"><div class="lw-mini-logo-thumb" role="img" aria-label="Indianapolis Colts Logo" style="background-image:url(&#039;https://logos-world.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Indianapolis-Colts-Logo-120x67.png&#039;);"></div><div class="lw-mini-logo-title">Indianapolis Colts Logo</div></a></article></div></div><style>.lw-mini-logos-section {
            margin: 26px 0 34px;
        }

        .lw-mini-logos-heading {
            margin: 0 0 22px;
            padding: 0 0 8px;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #a40a0e;
            font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            line-height: 1;
            color: #a40a0e;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .lw-mini-logos-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
            gap: 18px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .lw-mini-logo-card {
            margin: 0;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e6e6e6;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 5px rgba(0,0,0,.05);
        }

        .lw-mini-logo-link {
            display: block;
            height: 145px;
            padding: 16px 10px 12px;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .lw-mini-logo-thumb {
            width: 120px;
            height: 67px;
            margin: 0 auto 13px auto;
            background-position: center center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: contain;
        }

        .lw-mini-logo-title {
            height: 38px;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Anton', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.08;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #111;
            text-align: center;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: -webkit-box;
            -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
        }

        .lw-mini-logo-link:hover .lw-mini-logo-title {
            color: #a40a0e;
        }

        @media (max-width: 991px) {
            .lw-mini-logos-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
                gap: 12px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 767px) {
            .lw-mini-logos-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
                gap: 8px;
            }

            .lw-mini-logo-link {
                height: 130px;
                padding: 12px 8px 10px;
            }

            .lw-mini-logo-thumb {
                margin: 0 auto 10px auto;
            }

            .lw-mini-logo-title {
                height: 34px;
                font-size: 13px;
                line-height: 1.05;
            }

            .lw-mini-logos-heading {
                font-size: 21px;
            }
        }</style><br /> <script type="litespeed/javascript" data-src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-6198270508662570"
     crossorigin="anonymous"></script><br />
